### Create Workspace

POST http://localhost:5000/api/workspaces
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Engineering Team",
  "description": "Main workspace for engineering"
}

###

GET http://localhost:5000/api/workspaces
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

###

GET http://localhost:5000/api/workspaces/WORKSPACE_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN

###

PUT http://localhost:5000/api/workspaces/WORKSPACE_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Workspace",
  "description": "Updated description"
}

###

DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/workspaces/WORKSPACE_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN